{
  "uuid": "7eeade5017b423a9ed6e2b3c3d20a3b0",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Control Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties and Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Involved in drafting of functional specifications and detailed design specification documentation.</p></li><li><p>Perform design and development of Software, PLC and Interfaces.</p></li><li><p>Perform software implementation, system integration, testing and commissioning of advanced control systems for e-commerce system, material handling system, airport baggage handling systems, in-flight catering systems, robot systems and parcel handling systems.</p></li><li><p>Provide end-user training and after-sales support.</p></li><li><p>Undertake additional tasks & responsibilities as and when required or instructed.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications and Skills Required:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor/Master Degree in Automation, Electronics, Computer Science, Computer Engineering, or IT.</p></li><li><p>Experience in automation software development.</p></li><li><p>Knowledge in Industrial Automation or a related field is advantageous.</p></li><li><p>Strong proficiency in software engineering is essential.</p></li><li><p>Experience with development of SCADA systems such as iFix, Citect, or Wonderware.</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with PLCs programming including Siemens, Rockwell, Mitsubishi, Beckhoff, and Omron is preferred.</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in configuring and optimizing Fieldbus systems such as ASI-Bus, DeviceNet, Profibus, Profinet, ControlNet, Ethernet/IP, EtherCat, and CClink.</p></li><li><p>Ability to collaborate effectively as a dynamic team player with strong interpersonal skills.</p></li><li><p>Experience in supplier/vendor management and leading small project teams with cross-disciplinary personnel.</p></li><li><p>Demonstrated eagerness to explore and study new technologies, and willingness to undertake challenging tasks. Creative, innovative, and results-oriented mindset.</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in maintaining proper documentation throughout the development process and engineering change process.</p></li><li><p>Good communication skills in English, both verbal and written.</p></li><li><p>Applicants must have the capability to work independently and possess a strong drive for technology.</p></li><li><p>Willingness to travel and work on overseas projects is mandatory.<br /></p></li></ul><p>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
